## 🗂️ .GITIGNORE COMPLETO PARA TRADING TERMINAL

```gitignore
# ============================================================
# TRADING TERMINAL — .gitignore
# ============================================================

# === SECRETOS (NUNCA COMMITEAR) ===
.env
.env.local
.env.production
.env.staging
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
secrets/
credentials/

# === PYTHON ===
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
